  }, "v18"), mdx("p", null, "Cho n\xEAn ta tr\xFAt c\u01A1n gi\u1EADn ta tr\xEAn ch\xFAng v\xEC m\xE1u m\xE0 ch\xFAng \u0111\u1ED5 ra tr\xEAn \u0111\u1EA5t v\xE0 v\xEC ch\xFAng \u0111\xE3 l\xE0m \xF4 d\u01A1 \u0111\u1EA5t do c\xE1c h\xECnh t\u01B0\u1EE3ng c\u1EE7a ch\xFAng. "), mdx("h6", {
